Value VERSION (\S+)
Value BUILD_ID (\d+)
Value BUILD_ON (.*)
Value COPYRIGHT (.+)
Value MODEL (.+)
Value SERIAL_NUMBER (\S+)
Value UPTIME (.+)

Start
  ^Version:\s+${VERSION}\s*$$
  ^Build\ ID:\s+${BUILD_ID}\s*$$
  ^Build\ on:\s+${BUILD_ON}\s*$$
  ^Copyright:\s+${COPYRIGHT}\s*$$
  ^HW\ model:\s+${MODEL}\s*$$
  ^HW\ S/N:\s+${SERIAL_NUMBER}\s*$$
  ^Uptime:\s+${UPTIME}\s*$$ -> Record
